data.description: This charming property is on the edge of Lakeside and El Cajon, and is a flag lot tucked well off of Winter Gardens Blvd, with mountain views. Fully finished oversized high-ceiling garage with EV charging station makes for a great workshop. Solar panels and large yard with fire pit and large metal gazebo / workshop with hanging television and fans and 50 amp RV outlet. Fully remodeled kitchen, updated main bedroom with walk-in closet and private bath, updated hardwood floors, dual-pane windows, newer roof,  AC/Heating unit and duct-work, asphalt driveway and recently replaced fencing. This home features a great open floorplan and is centrally located.
